        <h2 class="fs-1 fw-bold">What is Pangia?</h2>
        <p>Pangia is an advanced knowledge environment designed to address the complex challenges posed by the climate crisis. Currently in an exploratory phase of development, Pangia plans to focus on three interconnected climate issues: (1) the loss of cultural heritage, (2) the dispersion and displacement of humanity, and (3) the disaggregation of essential scientific information. By providing a trusted, comprehensible, and coherent information platform, Pangia will engage the public and scholars to discover new knowledge and share information across generations.</p>
